text: @FedExHelp I lost a package. It was marked delivered on 21st July but I didn't receive it. My claim was rejected because I didn't request a signature. I've been calling the local office and visiting them but it's been of no use. I've been trying for 2 months now.

This is very stressful & it's been long since I've been hunting for my box. This was absolutely NOT the kind of customer service that I expected from @FedEx. The box was sent from College Park, Maryland to San Jose, California. 4 of the 5 boxes were delivered fine on 20th July.
